BT 0 g /F2 15 Tf 180.0 750 Td (THE RESEARCH BEHIND HAPPY MARRIAGES) Tj ET
q 0.3 G 0.5 w 72 738 m 540 738 l S Q
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 72 710 Td (After decades of research on thousands of couples, key principles emerged:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 72 692 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 72 674 Td (Happy couples are not perfect - they handle conflict differently.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 72 656 Td (They build deep friendship, maintain positive interactions,) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 72 638 Td (and repair quickly after disagreements.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 72 620 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 72 602 Td (The Magic Ratio: 5 positive interactions for every 1 negative.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 72 584 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 72 566 Td (The Four Horsemen that predict divorce:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 72 548 Td (  1. Criticism \(attacking character, not behavior\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 72 530 Td (  2. Contempt \(disgust, superiority, disrespect\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 72 512 Td (  3. Defensiveness \(counter-attacking, playing victim\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 72 494 Td (  4. Stonewalling \(shutting down, withdrawing\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 72 476 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 72 458 Td (The Antidotes:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 72 440 Td (  1. Gentle startup \(I feel... about... I need...\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 72 422 Td (  2. Build culture of appreciation) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 72 404 Td (  3. Take responsibility) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 72 386 Td (  4. Self-soothe, then re-engage) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 72 368 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 72 350 Td (This workbook guides you through building each principle.) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
