BT 0 g /F1 9 Tf 72 652 Td (4. Let me start again in a softer way.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 9 Tf 72 636 Td (5. I love you. This is hard but we'll get through it.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 9 Tf 72 620 Td (6. Tell me what you need right now.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 9 Tf 72 604 Td (7. I'm getting flooded. I need 20 minutes.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 9 Tf 72 588 Td (8. Can I have a do-over?) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 9 Tf 72 572 Td (9. You're right. I hadn't thought of it that way.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 9 Tf 72 556 Td (10. I appreciate you telling me how you feel.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 9 Tf 72 540 Td (11. One thing I admire about you is...) Tj ET
